OL,5, People's inability to afford essential 
OL,6, hygiene products is leaving many too   
OL,7, ashamed to go to work, a charity says. 
OL,9,FA report suggests 3.2 million UK adults
OL,10,Fare affected by so-called hygiene      
OL,11,Fpoverty - with 12% saying they have    
OL,12,Favoided facing colleagues as a result. 
OL,14,FTheir struggle to buy basic items such 
OL,15,Fas soap and deodorant is having a      
OL,16,Fdevastating effect on their daily      
OL,17,Flives, it says.                        
OL,19,FHygiene Bank chief executive Ruth Brock
OL,20,Fsaid it was a "hidden crisis".         
